<subSubSection id="E3F4D80624AEE4644143373B8913ABF8" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804" type="notes">
<paragraph id="55B0132B6E8B6BB84F09E8C8D1532A37" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="928E660DA9A99FA55046E0737195F318" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804">
<bibRefCitation id="DD6BB5587C820B9AC7945DC2EC737B68" author="Moon, C. S." journalOrPublisher="Korean Journal of Soil Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804" pagination="66 - 84" refId="B7742445" refString="Moon, C. S., Paik, J. C., 2006. Notes on Harpalini (Coleoptera, Carabidae) from Korea (3). Korean Journal of Soil Zoology 11 (1-2): 66 - 84" title="Notes on Harpalini (Coleoptera, Carabidae) from Korea (3)" volume="11" year="2006">Moon and Paik (2006c)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned that the Korean specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="38AB2BDFA395564D1677EE540355DF66" class="Insecta" genus="T." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="T. lucidus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucidus">
<emphasis id="F514AB54EEA4B19FD9E261076781B270" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804">T. lucidus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was not identified during the study. However, the brief collection data and photography of this species in Korea was recently recorded by 
<bibRefCitation id="761AB9898017D6BA1A62B6224B211C7F" author="Kwon, Tae Sung" journalOrPublisher="National Institute of Forest Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804" refId="B7862213" refString="Kwon, Tae Sung, Jung, Jong Kook, Park, Chan Woo, 2018. Coleoptera (Carabidae) specimen in National Institute of Forest Science, Korea. National Institute of Forest Science" title="Coleoptera (Carabidae) specimen in National Institute of Forest Science, Korea" year="2018">Kwon et al. (2018)</bibRefCitation>
, based on the specimen deposited in the National Institute of Forest Science, Korea. The specimen was re-examined by the authors and the distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="5AA5C0A63F7B705B046CA21C593CC24E" class="Insecta" genus="T." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="T. lucidus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucidus">
<emphasis id="097619A3C50935C527C8941EB6477941" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804">T. lucidus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in Korea is confirmed (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="F8E58EF15BDA3683604111D31854838E" captionStart="Figure 8" captionStartId="F7878775" captionText="Figure 8. Habitus of Trichotichnus (Iridessus) lucidus (Morawitz, 1863), male. Scale bar: 2 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.10.e83804.figure8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/683505" pageId="0" pageNumber="83804">8</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
